\par 
\par }{\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 In Chapter 9 you will remember that it was mentioned several definitions used in C.P.M., and here we will restate them in detail, together with several new ones.
\par 
\par }\pard \qj\fi-2880\li2880\nowidctlpar\tx-720\tx0\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\hyphpar0\adjustright {\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 Activity:\tab \tab \tab A time-consuming effort needs to complete a segment of the project. An activity is sometimes called a job and is shown by an arrow. Resources may or may not be required.
