\par 
\par }\pard \qj\fi-2880\li2880\nowidctlpar\tx-720\tx0\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\hyphpar0\adjustright {\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 Event:\tab \tab \tab A point in time indicating the beginning or the end of an activity. It is sometimes called a node and is indicated by a circle.
\par }\pard \qj\nowidctlpar\tx-720\hyphpar0\adjustright {\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 
\par 
\par }\pard \qj\fi-2880\li2880\nowidctlpar\tx-720\tx0\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\hyphpar0\adjustright {\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 Dummy:\tab \tab \tab A symbol showing a restraint relationship between activities. A dummy requires no time and is indicated by a dashed arrow.
