\par 
\par }\pard \qj\fi-2880\li2880\nowidctlpar\tx-720\tx0\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\hyphpar0\adjustright {\f0\expnd0\expndtw-3\lang3081 Earliest Start Time (ES):\tab The earliest time at which an activity can start, controlled by the earliest event time.
