\par It will be seen that the critical path lies between events 1, 5, 7, 11, 13 and 15 (note: an alternative numbering system has been used to facilitate possible future alterations) and the critical activities are A.D.F.G. and H. giving a total project duration of 160 minutes, which is the shortest time that work can be completed under these conditions.
\par 
\par Our Time Bar Diagram should be as follows:
